Phobias baby relayed the shake back to him
"Good girl now find a reason to get away from the maniac and get here 
quickly as possible."
he turned and walked back to the transport bay replacing the lock on 
an open crate. "computer activate all security locks to my signal." 
the computer clicked and whired as the security protocals locked into 
place. If he was going to have other Predacons on board he wouldn't 
have them snooping around.
